    <spirit:description>The CHI SNI interface is used by IO subordinate nodes. The SNI interface consists of the following VCs:
 - RXREQ
 - TXRSP
 - RXDAT
 - TXDAT
An SNI node receives request messages from the interconnect and returns response messages to it on the RXREQ and TXRSP channels. The data messages are exchanged with the interconnect on the TXDAT and RXDAT channels.
For more information please refer to the AMBA CHI Specification.</spirit:description>
